{
  "texts": [
    "This systematic approach allowed us to identify important themes, capture critical insights from the data, and effectively meet our research goals by comprehensively understanding the participants' perspectives.",
    "We found three themes and several subthemes and aligned them with our study's research questions.",
    "The qualitative interview data were analyzed using thematic analysis and the inductive technique.",
    "Thematic analysis is a technique for extensively and methodically analyzing qualitative data (Braun & Clarke, 2006).",
    "The data were then compiled and triangulated by data type and attributes."
  ]
}